    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>12" LPs, CDs, press kits, publicity items and photographs. The collection includes over 5,000 sound recordings documenting hip-hop music, primarily from the 1980s and 1990s in the United States.</p>  </scopecontent>
